name: MetaXCosmos
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
The META X COSMOS team is committed to building a highly secure and reputable Metaverse project. Through the governance of DAO, community members participate in project decision-making to ensure fairness and transparency. Any problems encountered during the development of the project and decisions made are all completed through community voting.

What makes your project unique?
Decentralized DAO management model

History of your project.
The blocknation team operates a blockchain tools website

What’s next for your project?
Increase the application of mobile APP to let more people know the blockchain.

What can your token be used for?
Token Trading, DAO Voting Pass
